Korea Hydro & Nuclear Sells $500 Million of 10-Year Bonds

-- B y   S h e l l e y   S m i t h
-- 
2011-07-07T01:21:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-07/korea-hydro-nuclear-sells-500-million-of-10-year-bonds.html
Korea Hydro & Nuclear Power Co. sold
$500 million of bonds due July 2021, according to data compiled
by Bloomberg.  Barclays Plc, Goldman Sachs Group Inc., Morgan Stanley and
Royal Bank of Scotland Group Plc managed the sale of the 4.75
percent notes. Samsung Securities Co. also helped arrange the
issue, the data show.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Shelley Smith  at 
 ssmith118@bloomberg.net  